Introducing Snooze. Whether a meeting is going to overrun, your train is delayed or you've inevitably decided to have just one more drink, it’s OK...plans change...just Snooze your journey from your app or your Watch and your driver will turn up a little later. Snooze is available when you pre-book journeys - take a look.

We also made some behind the scenes bug fixes and improvements.

CycleCab – Our cyclist pick up service that gets you and your bike home. Whether it is because of bad weather, a tough day at the office or you have had one too many at the local pub, CycleCab allows cyclists across London to stow their bikes in the back of their Addison Lee.

Some performance improvements have also been made to ensure the app is always running at 100%

Times change, but one thing hasn’t: our commitment to putting your journey first. The result? A car service that is only ever 'at your service'.
Now we have a new look to match our service. We hope you like it, and we look forward to being at your service very soon.
Our expertise in transport logistics means we also have a top quality courier service. Whether it’s a document or a sofa, you can now order a courier directly through our app.
